text: Raymond Protti is a University of Alberta graduate with a BA and MA in economics. Protti was the director of the Canadian Security Intelligence Service (CSIS) from 1992 through 1994.http://www.csis- scrs.gc.ca/hstrrtfcts/hstr/brfwrkngndx-eng.asp He has previously held positions as President and CEO of the Canadian Bankers Association, and Deputy Minister of Agriculture and Agri-food and of Labour Canada. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Directors of the Canadian Security Intelligence Service Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
